            "text": "Following a historic cut in early 2024 to realign its capital allocation and strengthen its balance sheet, the current payout ratio is much lower and considered more sustainable against current cash flows, though ongoing turnaround execution remains a primary risk."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "When does Walgreens pay its dividend?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
